                        Embassy.</item>
                    <item>
                        <hi rend="italic">Aide:</hi> Captain James Garfield, U. S. A.</item>
                    <item>
                        <hi rend="italic">Confidential Secretary:</hi> Mr. Richard C. Sweet.</item>
